name: ARIES - Keeper of the White Diamond Star
description:
ARIES
Harness the fiery warrior energy of Aries to burn away uncertainty & reveal the diamond clarity you seek. Be brave. The correct path is the one that scares you the most. Aries is a way-shower, a trailblazer, a pioneer whose determined focus to achieve her goals is second to none. Aries does the undoable, she laughs at the word "impossible" because she knows that if she can dream it, she can do it. Use your imagination to manifest your desires. Don't let fear stop you -feel the fear and do it anyway!
